 |&nbsp;475 West 260 North Orem, UT 84057</h4>\n\n<p>Our Orem, Utah Respite Care Nights are located within the Kids On The Move building. &nbsp;We are so thankful for the opportunity to hold respite in such a beautiful building, perfectly designed for the children in our program. Children and volunteers get to play in a large area that includes playrooms, an enclosed outside playground, and an exciting sensory room. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4>LEHI, UT |&nbsp;850 South 1700 West Lehi, UT 84043</h4>\n\n<p>Our Lehi, Utah Respite Care Nights are held within the Kids On The Move satellite location. &nbsp;This satellite location is a trailer on the grounds of Snow Spring Elementary School. &nbsp;The trailer is located on the South East side of Snow Springs Elementary and has Kids On The Move signage. &nbsp;This lovely little space is perfect for children with special needs and has a playroom and a sensory room. &nbsp;When the weather is nice volunteers and kids can go outside and play on Snow Springs Elementary&rsquo;s playground. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4>Springville, UT |&nbsp;451 S. Main St. Suites 3 &amp; 4 Springville, UT 84663</h4>\n\n<p>Our Springville, Utah Respite Care Nights are held within the TURN Community Services building. We are so grateful for this partnership with TURN and the opportunity to hold respite within such a beautiful building that is designed for individuals with special needs. &nbsp;Children and volunteers get to play with fun toys and play dough, color, and dance to music in a great atmosphere. &nbsp;</p>\n\n<h4>St. George, UT |&nbsp;398 E. Tabernacle St. George, UT 84770</h4>\n\n<p>Our KOTM Respite Care Center in St. George provides care for children with special needs while their caregivers receive a break to relieve stress, renew energy, and restore balance. Volunteers help children with activities that include&nbsp;crafts, Play-doh, games, and a movie at the end of the night. Held&nbsp;one Friday night each month from 6 p.m. to 9:30 p.m. We&nbsp;love the St. George area!</p>\n',1,'https://www.childplus.net/apply/en-us/83DA3460C8B342FA4781195B3D29561E/C73EF6D9004CEA495946B94C3402EEAE','Apply Now');
